274
00:19:34,350 --> 00:19:35,350
Did she submit this?

275
00:19:35,440 --> 00:19:38,190
Yes. It's a written statement
submitted by Park Sujeong.

276
00:19:40,770 --> 00:19:42,230
She wrote down a lot.

277
00:19:44,110 --> 00:19:45,110
What does it say?

278
00:19:46,450 --> 00:19:49,870
