and verbally abusive during the marriage.

279
00:19:54,960 --> 00:19:56,620
DEFENDANT WAS PHYSICALLY ASSAULTED

280
00:19:56,710 --> 00:19:58,210
DEFENDANT WAS VERBALLY ABUSED

281
00:20:03,210 --> 00:20:05,510
