based on their living conditions.

322
00:23:09,480 --> 00:23:12,320
In this case, neither the plaintiff
nor the defendants

323
00:23:12,400 --> 00:23:14,820
are the real parties here.

324
00:23:15,410 --> 00:23:18,780
If anything,
they're all just victims of the affair.

325
00:23:23,460 --> 00:23:24,460
Let's do this.

326
00:23:24,540 --> 00:23:27,460
We'll schedule a preparatory hearing,

327
00:23:27,540 --> 00:23:30,460
and I'll try to mediate directly then,

328
00:23:30,550 --> 00:23:33,470
so make sure both the plaintiff
and the defendants attend.

329
00:23:35,180 --> 00:23:37,800
