330
00:23:38,390 --> 00:23:40,350
Just have Lee Sujin attend.

331
00:23:41,890 --> 00:23:43,850
Yes, Your Honor.
I'll talk to the plaintiff.

332
00:23:47,150 --> 00:23:51,070
