335
00:23:54,780 --> 00:23:56,200
Yes, Your Honor.

336
00:23:56,280 --> 00:23:58,070
The same goes for plaintiff's counsel.

337
00:23:58,160 --> 00:23:59,370
Yes, Your Honor. I will.

